they make me Governor of India, GÃ©rard, Iâ€™ll make you Minister of
Kashmirâ€”thatâ€™s settled. Vive lâ€™Empereur! Hurrah! hurrah! hurrah! The
Cossacksâ€”those rascalsâ€”see how they run! Vive lâ€™Empereur! There he
