â€œItâ€™s very nice, your excellency! Wouldnâ€™t you like to?â€ said he.

â€œItâ€™s dirty,â€ replied Prince Andrew, making a grimace.

â€œWeâ€™ll clear it out for you in a minute,â€ said TimÃ³khin, and, still
