On the seventh of August Prince BagratiÃ³n wrote as follows from his
quarters at MikhÃ¡ylovna on the SmolÃ©nsk road:

Dear Count AlÃ©xis AndrÃ©evichâ€”(He was writing to ArakchÃ©ev but knew that
