even increased to desperation like a man who, straining himself, shrieks
with all his remaining strength.





CHAPTER XXXIII

The chief action of the battle of BorodinÃ³ was fought within the seven
thousand feet between BorodinÃ³ and BagratiÃ³nâ€™s flÃ¨ches. Beyond that
