â€œGet into step, FÃ«dor... I say, FÃ«dor!â€ said the foremost peasant.

â€œNow thatâ€™s right!â€ said the one behind joyfully, when he had got into
step.

â€œYour excellency! Eh, Prince!â€ said the trembling voice of TimÃ³khin, who
