blood-stained smith stood beside him with a gloomy face. A drone of
voices was audible through the closed window.

â€œIs my carriage ready?â€ asked RostopchÃ­n, stepping back from the window.

â€œIt is, your excellency,â€ replied the adjutant.

RostopchÃ­n went again to the balcony door.

â€œBut what do they want?â€ he asked the superintendent of police.

â€œYour excellency, they say they have got ready, according to your
