NatÃ¡sha drew closer to him. Her face shone with rapturous joy.

â€œNatÃ¡sha, I love you too much! More than anything in the world.â€

â€œAnd I!â€â€”She turned away for an instant. â€œWhy too much?â€ she asked.

â€œWhy too much?... Well, what do you, what do you feel in your soul, your
