and his round face seemed rounder and pleasanter than ever.

â€œA promise is own brother to performance! I said Friday and here it is,
ready,â€ said PlatÃ³n, smiling and unfolding the shirt he had sewn.

The Frenchman glanced around uneasily and then, as if overcoming his
