DenÃ­sovâ€™s horse swerved aside to avoid a pool in the track and bumped
his riderâ€™s knee against a tree.

â€œOh, the devil!â€ exclaimed DenÃ­sov angrily, and showing his teeth he
struck his horse three times with his whip, splashing himself and his
